INT. SPACESHIP BRIDGE - DAY #1#

Consoles blink in rhythmic patterns. CAPTAIN OYELARAN studies a star chart.

EXT. SPACESHIP - ESTABLISHING #2#

The vessel drifts silently against a field of stars.

INT. ENGINE ROOM - CONTINUOUS #3#

Sparks fly from an exposed panel. An engineer curses under his breath.

INT. SPACESHIP BRIDGE - LATER #1A#

Captain Oyelaran hasn't moved from the chart in hours.

CAPTAIN OYELARAN
Get me engineering.
